# Testing & DVT

## Unit tests (mandatory)

- Every **created or modified** code file must have a matching `*_test.go` (or equivalent) validating the change.
- Tests must reflect real behavior, not trivial assertions.
- Run tests before marking work complete.

## Technical debt registry

For each **new feature or capability**, add an entry to `docs/DVT.md`:

```markdown
## DVT-XX: Short title
- **Scope**: package/path
- **Added**: YYYY-MM-DD
- **Needs**: integration/e2e test description for production parity
- **Status**: open
```

- Increment IDs sequentially: DVT-01, DVT-02, …
- One DVT per distinct new functionality.
